Description: PyMoDAQ Plugins
        ###############
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/pymodaq_plugins.svg
           :target: https://pypi.org/project/pymodaq_plugins/
           :alt: Latest Version
        
        .. image:: https://readthedocs.org/projects/pymodaq/badge/?version=latest
